description:
The Fayda application developed as a part of the Reaction Roulette m/q LDRD project (76006) primarily exists as a data
visualization, analysis and predictive platform for data collected using atomic tandem inductively coupled plasma mass
spectrometry (ICP-MS/MS)
name: Fayda
